(US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>A propriedade <strong><code>HTMLElement.contentEditable </code></strong>é usada para indicar se o elemento é editável ou não. Esse atributo enumerado pode ter os seguintes valores:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>\"true\"</code> Indica que o elemento é editável;</li>\n <li><code>\"false\"</code> Indica que o elemento não pode ser editável;</li>\n <li><code>\"inherit\"</code> Indica que o elemento herda o status editável de seu pai.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Você pode usar a propriedade <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/isContentEditable\"><code>HTMLElement.isContentEditable</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> para testar o valor calculado <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> desta propriedade.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>editable</em> = element.contentEditable element.contentEditable= \"true\"\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificação","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/interaction.html#contenteditable\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'contenteditable' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>11</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3\" title=\"Released on 2008-06-17.\">3.0</a> (1.9)</td>\n   <td>6<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td>10.6</td>\n   <td>3.2</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>3</td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.9)</td>\n   <td>6<sup>[1]</sup></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>5</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Internet Explorer has a bunch of bugs regarding the implementation of this feature. IE10 crashes in some cases when editing lists (<a href=\"https://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedback/details/796187/internet-explorer-10-crash-with-contenteditable-list\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 796187</a>). IE11+ uses invalid positioning for caret when an element is floated (<a href=\"https://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedback/details/858749\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 858749</a>). In IE9-10 the window freezes when using mousewheel while dragging (<a href=\"https://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedbackdetail/view/809254\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 809254</a>). IE10-11 does not fire the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/input_event\"><code>input</code></a> event (<a href=\"https://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedbackdetail/view/794285\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 794285</a>). IE10 crashes after selecting \"Cut\" from the context menu (<a href=\"https://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedbackdetail/view/801770\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 801770</a>). IE11+ does not allow placing the caret in an empty table cell (<a href=\"https://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedbackdetail/view/807199\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 807199</a>). IE10 does not fire <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/contextmenu_event\"><code>contextmenu</code></a> event when right-clicking on misspelled words (<a href=\"https://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedbackdetail/view/774350\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 774350</a>). IE11 appends <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/br\"><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></a> elements to <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a> when showing/hiding an <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a> with contenteditable document inside (<a href=\"https://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedbackdetail/view/864804\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 864804</a>). IE11 does not allow disabling resize handles for images/inputs (<a href=\"https://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedbackdetail/view/907422\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug 907422</a>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/isContentEditable\"><code>HTMLElement.isContentEditable</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes/contenteditable\">contenteditable</a> global attribute.</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://medium.com/medium-eng/why-contenteditable-is-terrible-122d8a40e480\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Why ContentEditable is Terrible, Or: How the Medium Editor Works</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"especificação"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A propriedade HTMLElement.contentEditable é usada para indicar se o elemento é editável ou não. Esse atributo enumerado pode ter os seguintes valores:","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLElement.contentEditable","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLElement.contentEditable","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTMLElement.contentEditable","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLElement.contentEditable","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLElement.contentEditable","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"HTMLElement.contentEditable","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLElement.contentEditable","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/htmlelement/contenteditable","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/htmlelement/contenteditable/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement","title":"HTMLElement"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/contentEditable","title":"HTMLElement.contentEditable"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLElement.contentEditable - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}